Name: Bio Bots
About the game: Bio Bots is a Free to play third-person team-based shooter. Enjoy playing chaotic matches in different game-modes such as: - Capture the points - Team-Deathmatch - Infinite Threat - Free For All - Rounds With the help of machinery to heal up, block shots, cause damage, or even to jump higher! Features -Multiple game modes -Multiple maps & weather options -Leveling & Missions -Character customization -Items Market Bio Bots is developed by myself; using Unity game engine
